<SUBJECT>
<P>
AGASSI, ANDRE; DRESS CODES; FRENCH OPEN (TENNIS TOURNAMENT); SPORTS RULES AND 
REGULATIONS 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA060290-0052 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 227731 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
June 2, 1990, Saturday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Sports; Part C; Page 7; Column 1; Sports Desk 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
<P>
33 words 
</P>
</LENGTH>
<HEADLINE>
<P>
NEWSWIRE 
</P>
