<TEXT>
<P>
Several Olympians and world-class athletes will compete in the Irvine Elite 
Classic track and field meet Sunday at UC Irvine. 
</P>
<P>
The meet, in its second year, will begin at 3:30 p.m. with the field events. 
</P>
<P>
Running events -- there will be no race longer than 800 meters -- begin with 
the women's 100-meter hurdles at 4:30. 
</P>
