Joaquim Cruz, the gold medalist in the 1984 Olympics; Jamaica's Grace Jackson, 
silver medalist in the 200 meters at the Seoul Olympics and U.S. Olympians 
Stanley Floyd (sprints), Doug Nordquist (high jump), LaTanya Sheffield 
(hurdles), Ramona Pagel and Bonnie Dasse (shot put), Mike Powell (long jump) 
and Karin Smith (javelin). 
</P>
<P>
Tickets, which are $10 for adults, $5 for UC Irvine students and children, can 
be purchased at the gate. 
