-- ISRAEL; TERRORISM -- ISRAEL; GUERRILLAS -- ISRAEL; ISRAEL -- FOREIGN 
RELATIONS -- PLO; UNITED STATES -- FOREIGN RELATIONS -- PLO; ISRAEL -- 
TERRITORIES AND POSSESSIONS; WEST BANK (ISRAEL); GAZA STRIP; ISRAEL -- REVOLTS; 
HUNGER STRIKES; DEMONSTRATIONS -- ISRAEL 
</P>
