BOND); PROPOSITION 111 (GASOLINE TAX); PROPOSITION 117 (WILDLIFE PROTECTION); 
MOUNTAIN LIONS; HUNTING; ANIMAL CONTROL; POLITICAL ENDORSEMENTS 
</P>
