POLITICAL CANDIDATES; POLITICAL CAMPAIGNS; INSURANCE INDUSTRY -- CALIFORNIA; 
ATTORNEYS; POLITICAL CONTRIBUTIONS; HEALTH INSURANCE; AUTOMOBILE INSURANCE; NO 
FAULT INSURANCE 
</P>
