<P>
MAGIC SHOW TO HELP LITTLE SMILES APPEAR 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Children from more than 30 children's hospitals and homes for abused and 
handicapped children will be treated to various feats of magic at the Miracle 
of Magic Show today at Anaheim High School. 
</P>
<P>
Organized by the Sunshine for Children Foundation, a nonprofit organization 
