<P>
Profile 
</P>
</TYPE>
<SUBJECT>
<P>
BASEBALL CHAMPIONSHIPS; HIGH SCHOOL ATHLETICS; BASEBALL PLAYERS; TUSTIN HIGH 
SCHOOL 
</P>
