Champlin after a second-inning out. ; Photo, Bearing down -- Stephanie Smith 
delivers a pitch in third inning of Garden Grove's 2-0 defeat. C15 JOHN FUNG / 
Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
