APARTMENTS -- ORANGE COUNTY; HOUSING -- ORANGE COUNTY; BUILDING INDUSTRY -- 
ORANGE COUNTY; NEWPORT PACIFIC DEVELOPMENT CORP 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
